abstract: Amazon workers in the eastern German city of Leipzig will extend until Christmas Eve their strike over pay and conditions, trade union Verdi said on Friday.
snippet: Amazon workers in the eastern German city of Leipzig will extend until Christmas Eve their strike over pay and conditions, trade union Verdi said on Friday.
lead_paragraph: BERLIN, Germany — Amazon workers in the eastern German city of Leipzig will extend until Christmas Eve their strike over pay and conditions, trade union Verdi said on Friday.

abstract: Italian spirits group Campari has agreed to buy the distributor of its brand portfolio in France for an enterprise value of 60 million euros (£51.04 million), the company said on Friday.

abstract: Johnson & Johnson said on Friday it would acquire the remaining stake in Verb Surgical Inc, from Verily, Alphabet Inc's life sciences division.

abstract: United Airlines Co is extending its cancellations of Boeing 737 MAX flights until June 4 as Boeing's top supplier, Spirit AeroSystems Inc, said it would stop making fuselages for the grounded jets.

abstract: The Bank of England should cut interest rates now, rather than risk the British economy slowing to a point where the central bank can do little to help it, policymaker Jonathan Haskel said on Friday.

abstract: Water downstream of a Rio Tinto mine in southern Madagascar contains high concentrations of uranium and lead, potentially endangering local residents who depend on a nearby lake and river for drinking water, a study released on Friday found.

headline_main: Water Around Rio Tinto's Madagascar Mine Is High in Lead, Uranium-Study
headline_print_headline: Water Around Rio Tinto's Madagascar Mine Is High in Lead, Uranium-Study
